OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,FA police officer who had her nose
OL,7,Fbroken during an attack at Manchester
OL,8,FAirport asked her attacker: "Could you
OL,9,Fsee how scared I was," as he was
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 21, was jailed
OL,13,Ffor three-and-a-half years at
OL,14,FLiverpool Crown Court after he was
OL,15,Fconvicted of assaulting two female
OL,16,Fpolice officers and a member of the
OL,17,Fpublic during the incident on 23 July
OL,18,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
