OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,FReading a victim impact statement
OL,7,Fduring Amaaz's sentencing, PC Ward
OL,8,Fdescribed herself at the time as a
OL,9,Ffemale who "weighed no more than eight
OL,10,Fstone."
OL,12,FShe said: "You are a male and you
OL,13,Fchose to attack me without a second
OL,14,Fthought.
OL,16,F"You chose to attack a female. You
OL,17,Fknocked me to the ground with one
OL,18,Fpunch, with so much force you broke my
OL,19,Fnose.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
