PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,F"How would you feel if a male did that
OL,7,Fto your mother?
OL,9,F"How would you feel if it was your
OL,10,Fmother standing here today explaining
OL,11,Fhow she was violently assaulted by a
OL,12,Fmale?
OL,14,F"What you did was cowardly."
OL,16,FPC Ward continued: "In the moments
OL,17,Fbefore you punched me, I remember you
OL,18,Flooked directly into my eyes.
OL,20,F"Could you see how scared I was? I was
OL,21,Fpetrified.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
