PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,F"I just remember hitting the floor and
OL,7,Fthinking 'this is it'. I felt instant
OL,8,Fpain and then I saw the blood. I
OL,9,Fdidn't know what was going on."
OL,11,FThree Greater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,12,Fofficers entered the Terminal 2 car
OL,13,Fpark pay station after reports that a
OL,14,Fmale fitting Amaaz's description had
OL,15,Fheadbutted a member of the public at a
OL,16,FStarbucks cafe in the airport minutes
OL,17,Fearlier.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
