PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,F"You are not a victim. I am the one
OL,7,Fwho was injured, not you. You had the
OL,8,Fwhole world listening to you and you
OL,9,Fshowed no remorse. Not one ounce."
OL,11,FThe brothers, both from Rochdale, said
OL,12,Ftheir actions were defensive rather
OL,13,Fthan offensive.
OL,15,FPC Ward said: "The things that have
OL,16,Fbeen written about me on social media
OL,17,Fare disgusting. Do I deserve to be
OL,18,Fspoken about in that way?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
