PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,F"I was made to feel like an idiot. You
OL,7,Fcould have stopped that by telling the
OL,8,Ftruth."
OL,10,FWard, who is now on maternity leave
OL,11,Fsaid: "Much of my maternity leave I
OL,12,Fhave had the worry of having to go
OL,13,Fback to court hanging over me.
OL,15,F"I have been unable to enjoy the
OL,16,Fexperience as I should have, and I
OL,17,Ffind this extremely unfair. I'll never
OL,18,Fget this time back.
OL,20,F"You deserve no more of my time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
