OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,FPC Ellie Cook, who Amaaz was also
OL,7,Fconvicted of assaulting after punching
OL,8,Fher a number of times, told the court
OL,9,Fshe had been "broken" following the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FPC Cook's victim impact statement was
OL,13,Fread on her behalf, stating that the
OL,14,Fincident has made her give up her
OL,15,Fdream of being a firearms officer.
OL,17,FThe statement said: "I don't think you
OL,18,Fwill ever begin to understand what you
OL,19,Fhave done to me, or my family. I used
OL,20,Fto be happy. I used to be driven. I
OL,21,Fused to be focused. I am now broken."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
