PN,36409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,FShe added: "I remember feeling punches
OL,7,Fin quick succession and with such
OL,8,Fpower behind them that I thought I was
OL,9,Fbeing attacked by 3-4 people. I was
OL,10,Fterrified.
OL,12,F"I quickly thought I'm in a bad place
OL,13,Fand I don't know how to get out of it.
OL,15,F"The pain was excruciating with each
OL,16,Fblow, my vision went black and I was
OL,17,Fso disorientated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
