PN,36410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,F"It's hard to explain what goes
OL,7,Fthrough your mind in a situation like
OL,8,Fthat, being attacked and then seeing
OL,9,Fnot only a colleague, but a friend, on
OL,10,Fthe floor bleeding."
OL,12,FPC Cook's statement explains that she
OL,13,Fwas signed off work for "duty-related
OL,14,Ftrauma".
OL,16,FShe said: "I lost so much weight
OL,17,Fbecause I couldn't eat. I couldn't
OL,18,Fopen my jaw, so I had to eat mushed up
OL,19,Ffood for a quite a while afterwards.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
