FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,F"I'm still physically suffering now. I
OL,7,Fhave shooting pains in my jaw whenever
OL,8,FI yawn, I have regular headaches, and
OL,9,FI still have trouble sleeping."
OL,11,FHer statement ended with: "It pains me
OL,12,Fto say this, but because of what you
OL,13,Fhave done to me I have decided to give
OL,14,Fup being a firearms officer. I just
OL,15,Fcan't face it at the minute.
OL,17,F"I hope the words I have read today
OL,18,Fstay with you for the rest of your
OL,19,Flives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
