OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782562706
OL,3,C'Could you see how scared I was?':
OL,4,CPolice officer asks airport attacker
OL,6,F"I hope you have flashbacks of what I
OL,7,Fam saying the way I have flash backs
OL,8,Fof that day.
OL,10,F"I hope you never forget, because I
OL,11,Fknow I won't. "
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
